  "detailed_description": "Winter Wastelands is a sci-fi fantasy action-adventure game about trying to escape the ice planet you crash-landed on.<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight through enemies and bosses with a sword and special abilities gained along the way.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Explore the 7 areas.</li></ul> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find new items and costumes to obtain special abilities.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Meet strange and vibrant characters.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Bright and colorful pixel art.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Programming, design, art, animation, and music all made by one person.</li></ul><br>Photosensitive Warning: This game contains sequences of flashing bright colors.",
